261
00:18:59,442 --> 00:19:03,150
This colorful piece of chert
is the hardest rock around.

262
00:19:03,233 --> 00:19:07,108
Which makes it the perfect
material to craft into a knife.

263
00:19:07,192 --> 00:19:11,025
Study everything.
