264
00:19:11,108 --> 00:19:13,025
[chuckles]

265
00:19:25,317 --> 00:19:28,442
I can unravel this plant
like string cheese.

266
00:19:33,525 --> 00:19:35,775
[MONKEY C] It looks like
he's twisting it now.

267
00:19:35,858 --> 00:19:40,150
[MONKEY B] I bet you his brain
is just as smooth as his skin.

268
00:19:48,483 --> 00:19:50,483
[SENKU]
Surprisingly enough,

269
00:19:50,567 --> 00:19:53,817
there are quite a few
animals that use tools.

270
00:19:53,900 --> 00:19:59,192
Crows, otters,
orangutans, and more.

271
00:19:59,275 --> 00:20:01,567
But out of all the
creatures in this world,

272
00:20:01,650 --> 00:20:04,275
only one can make
use of science.

273
00:20:05,775 --> 00:20:07,442
[SENKU] When cellulose
is heated through friction

274
00:20:07,525 --> 00:20:11,275
and exposed to air, it rapidly
oxidizes, giving us...

275
00:20:11,358 --> 00:20:14,942
[MONKEYS scream]

276
00:20:15,025 --> 00:20:16,483
[SENKU]
...combustion!

277
00:20:32,525 --> 00:20:35,108
[SENKU screams]

278
00:20:41,483 --> 00:20:42,775
[growls]

279
00:20:49,067 --> 00:20:50,233
[MONKEY B]
Huh?

280
00:20:54,400 --> 00:20:57,067
[SENKU] Through persistence
and ingenuity,

281
00:20:57,150 --> 00:21:00,442
I can take everything this
universe has to offer.

282
00:21:04,358 --> 00:21:06,608
I'm the master of science!

283
00:21:34,858 --> 00:21:37,775
[ALL gasping]

284
00:21:47,275 --> 00:21:49,192
[SENKU chuckles]

285
00:21:49,275 --> 00:21:53,108
[SENKU] Just realized I
never introduced myself.

286
00:21:53,192 --> 00:21:56,108
It's a pleasure to meet you all.

287
00:21:56,192 --> 00:21:58,525
[MONKEY C]
Ah! What the hell is that?

288
00:21:58,608 --> 00:22:02,108
[MONKEY B] The shiny monkey
isn't shiny anymore!

289
00:22:03,192 --> 00:22:04,567
[SENKU]
You see,

290
00:22:04,650 --> 00:22:08,275
I'm the only one of my kind
still walking this world.

291
00:22:08,358 --> 00:22:10,442
I'm a human being.

292
00:22:13,567 --> 00:22:16,108
[SENKU] I intend to build a
technological civilization

293
00:22:16,192 --> 00:22:17,942
from scratch.

294
00:22:18,025 --> 00:22:20,733
And this is where it all starts.

